headline: Why GitLab (GTLB) Shares Are Plunging Today
summary: Shares of devSecOps platform provider GitLab (NASDAQ:GTLB) fell 5.7% in the afternoon session after investors took profits following a significant rally in the previous session, which was fueled by takeover rumors that were later met with skepticism.
